title: Ep. 2764 - Tapu Sena Is Struggling - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 1 July 2019
shortDesc: Tapu Sena plans to repair Bhide's broken tuition board. They try in many places but the board is still not repaired. They don't have much time as Bhide must be coming at any time. Keep watching!

title: Ep. 2765 - Bhide Is Furious - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 2 July 2019
shortDesc: Tapu Sena fails to repair Bhide's tuition board. Bhide comes to know and is furious on Tapu, his friends and even on Jethalal. WIll Bhide understand? Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2766 - Tapu Sena And The Tuition Board - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 3 July 2019
shortDesc: Tapu Sena is trying very hard to repair Bhide's broken tuition board. Madhvi has sent Bhide to the market and along with Mrs. Hathi, she is assisting the boys. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2767 - Baga Spills The Beans - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 4 July 2019
shortDesc: Tappu gets a hair dryer from Babita and tries to dry the paint on Bhide's tuition board. Jethalal asks Bagha with whom he was talking on the phone. Jethalal and Nattu Kaka accuse him of talking with Bawari and ask him to show his phone.

title: Ep. 2768 - The New Tuition Board - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 5 July 2019
shortDesc: While Tapu and his friends are worried over the board and are struggling hard to repair it, Bhide surprises them by showing them the new tuition board. He tells them that he was aware of their efforts. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2769 - Jethalal Meets Babita - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 8 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal wears the best shirt of his collection for which once he had got appreciated by Babita. But while getting out of the house, gets collided with Champaklal and somehow rescues to continue for the shop. He meets Babita on the way. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2770 - Bagha Bunks Duty - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 9 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal warns Bagha not to spend time with Bawri but Bawri drops in the shop in Jethalal's absence. Bagha leaves the shop with Bawri to spend some time with her. Jethalal is yet to know about this. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2771 - Natu Kaka Scolds Bagha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 10 July 2019
shortDesc: Bagha's duty in the shop gets hampered when he spends time with Bawri. Natu Kaka who had taken his responsibility gets angry with his activities. Bawri also gets upset. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2772 - Bagha And Natu Kaka - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 11 July 2019
shortDesc: There was a fallout between Natu Kaka and Bagha due to which both have stopped talking to each other. Jethalal comes to know about this and is worried because business is getting hampered. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2773 - Bagha Quarrels With Natu Kaka - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 12 July 2019
shortDesc: Bagha and Natu Kaka fight over who will watch the TV in the room. Bagha is not letting Natu Kaka watch the news and both refuse to compromise on this trivial matter. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2774 - Jethalal In Dilemma - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 15 July 2019
shortDesc: Bagha and Natu Kaka call Jethalal at midnight and tell him to come to their place to resolve their quarrel. Jethalal hesitatingly agrees and arrives at their place only to see them too adamant to compromise. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2775 - The Fight Continues - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 16 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal tries to solve the fight between Bagh and Natu Kaka but everything goes wrong when they don't listen to Jethalal's advice. when both Bagha and Natu Kaka present their views in front of Jethalal a new fight emerges.

title: Ep. 2776 - Bhide Is Blamed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 17 July 2019
shortDesc: Suspecting of a theft in the clubhouse in the society, everyone is worried. Popatlal blames Bhide for the mishap as Bhide is the secretary of the society. Bhide resigns from the post. Stay tuned!

title: Ep. 2777 - Bagha Gets Late - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 18 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal gets angry on Bagha and Nattu Kaka as they arrive late to shop and misses a good customer. On asking, Nattu Kaka escapes by saying Bagha is having the shop's key but when Bagha arrives, gives a very silly reason. What is the reason?

title: Ep. 2778 - Champaklal's Idea - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - 19 July 2019
shortDesc: Jethalal is still worried because of Bagha and Nattu Kaka, Champaklal calls him and gives him an idea to resolve this quarrel between Bagha and Natu Kaka. To know what this idea is, stay tuned!
